11005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945200/extras/fc7cee132f67392355721051c443466e.poster.avif?t=1764411005\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945200/extras/fc7cee132f67392355721051c443466e.webm?t=1764411005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945200/extras/fc7cee132f67392355721051c443466e.mp4?t=1764411005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build relationships with characters by progressing their stories and helping them out with favors.</h2></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945200/extras/ae2a31b4a11579fc81771b3a69d385be.avif?t=1764411005\" width=626 height=354 /></span><br><br>You can progress character stories in whichever order you prefer,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945200/extras/78708b4a297942ad1607a05b8292069c.avif?t=1764411005\" width=626 height=244 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>One thing I like to convey to the player is the character's emotions while speaking. So I created, and hand-pick face emotes to give every line of dialogue more impact.<br></li><li>I also utilize different kinds of screen transitions depending on the context of the scene/dialogue to make them more lively.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945200/extras/a0ce30a981ddaeb3f477b111eb9d8666.poster.avif?t=1764411005\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co